OL,3,CWhy zero net migration may not be
OL,4,Cpossible or desirable
OL,6,FNigel Farage has a point.
OL,8,FImmigration was at the heart of the
OL,9,FBrexit debate. A desire to control the
OL,10,Fnumber of people arriving in the UK is
OL,11,Fwhat drove the vote to leave the EU.
OL,13,FThe fact which got lost in the heat of
OL,14,Fthe referendum campaign was that most
OL,15,Fof the immigration was not from the
OL,16,FEU. Today that's even truer.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G1/15
