OL,3,CWhy zero net migration may not be
OL,4,Cpossible or desirable
OL,6,FThere are strong feelings about
OL,7,Fimmigration and some of it is easy to
OL,8,Funderstand. The increase in
OL,9,Fimmigration has been very rapid in
OL,10,FBritain and, at the margins, some of
OL,11,Fit may have been regressive.
OL,13,FFirst generation immigrants tend to
OL,14,Ftake lower skilled jobs and the
OL,15,Fevidence suggests that may have had a
OL,16,Fsmall dampeningfor the lowest paid.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G2/15
