OL,3,CWhy zero net migration may not be
OL,4,Cpossible or desirable
OL,6,FAnd that's the problem with
OL,7,Fimmigration. It affects huge parts of
OL,8,Four economy in complicated ways, far
OL,9,Fmore complicated than politicians
OL,10,Fpresent. And a single target ignores
OL,11,Fthat complexity.
OL,13,FHave you heard our new podcast Talking
OL,14,FPolitics? Every week Tom, Robert and
OL,15,FAnushka dig into the biggest issues
OL,16,Fdominating the political agenda...
OL,18,FIfwere somehow achieved, it would also
OL,19,Fleave the UK's population in slight
OL,20,Fdecline.
