OL,3,CWhy zero net migration may not be
OL,4,Cpossible or desirable
OL,6,FThe birth rate fell to 1.49 children
OL,7,Fper woman in 2022, well below the 2.1
OL,8,Fneeded to maintain a steady population
OL,9,Fwithout significant immigration.
OL,11,FA shrinking population need not be an
OL,12,Feconomic disaster but there would be
OL,13,Fconsequences for how long people work
OL,14,Fand what sort of care they can expect
OL,15,Fthe (smaller) state to provide as they
OL,16,Fage.
OL,18,FFarage never talks about these trade-
OL,19,Foffs. He also rarely speaks about the
OL,20,Fbenefits of immigration but they exist
OL,21,Ftoo.
