OL,6,FBusinesses in some sectors of the
OL,7,Feconomy - , retail, construction,
OL,8,Fagriculture in technology and
OL,9,Fcommunications - will tell you that
OL,10,Fthey depend on migrant labour.
OL,12,FMigrant labour keeps the show on the
OL,13,Froad for the NHS and in care homes
OL,14,Facross the UK.
OL,16,FAlmost one in five workers in the UK
OL,17,Fwere not born here.
