OL,3,CWhy zero net migration may not be
OL,4,Cpossible or desirable
OL,6,FThe number of UK born people who are
OL,7,Feconomically inactive has risen since
OL,8,Fthe pandemic and a record number now
OL,9,Fsay ill-health prevents them from
OL,10,Fworking.
OL,12,FSupporting people to move off benefits
OL,13,Fand back into the workforce is
OL,14,Fperfectly sensible but it takes time.
OL,16,FWhy? Because once again, it's
OL,17,Fcomplicated. Although Nigel Farage
OL,18,Fdoes make everything sound very
OL,19,Fstraightforward.
